regimes database documentation

regimes.Rd

regimes database documentation

Usage

regimes

Format

The regimes database is a list that contains the following 1 datasets: IRD. For more information and references to each of the datasets used, please use the data_source() and data_contrast() functions.

IRD:

A dataset with 92 observations and the following 7 variables: Regime, RegimeComponent, Beg, Wat, Wat2, End, RegimeElement.
